  <span id="freeText14214832930527983155" style="display:none">Definitely not my favourite so far; things felt a little too coincidental and almost silly at times. <s>I'm hanging out for more appearances from Jarlaxle tbh.</s><br />Proper review to come later when I'm not tired AF.<br /><br />Also: I love this world a lot, but the series reaaaaally needs some more well-rounded female characters. Catti-Brie has a few appearances, but the only other female characters are unnamed 'womenfolk' (who are treated like damsels in distress at best and 'seen but not heard' burdens at worst) and the mindless, tortured harem/slave girls the evil wizard keeps and routinely assaults in his tower. Not the best nor the most diverse range of female characters, but I'm hoping it gets better as the series progresses!</span>
