              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7686556549341378939">Great lightweight fantasy. A must-read for any D&amp;D players. The first book in the Icewind Dale and Legend of Drizzt series. <br/>(Note: This book is considered book 4 of the Drizzt series but that is because <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1023510.R_A__Salvatore' title='R.A. Salvatore' rel='nofollow noopener'>R.A. Salvatore</a> went back and added a backstory for Drizzt, his dark elf hero.)</span>
  <span id="freeText7686556549341378939" style="display:none">Great lightweight fantasy. A must-read for any D&amp;D players. The first book in the Icewind Dale and Legend of Drizzt series. <br />(Note: This book is considered book 4 of the Drizzt series but that is because <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/1023510.R_A__Salvatore" title="R.A. Salvatore" rel="nofollow noopener">R.A. Salvatore</a> went back and added a backstory for Drizzt, his dark elf hero.)</span>
