<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div><div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><div class="extraHeader"><a class="actionLinkLite" rel="nofollow" href="/topic/new?context_id=66693&amp;context_type=Book">new topic</a></div><a href="/topic/list_book/66693.The_Crystal_Shard">Discuss This Book</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent"><table cellspacing='0' class='tableList uitext bookDiscussions' width='100%'>
<tr>
