</tr>

	<tr>
		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Project Realms Reads" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/21743025-the-crystal-shard-by-r-a-salvatore-the-icewind-dale-trilogy-1-the-leg">Project Realms Reads:</a>
        </b>
      
